
:::: Micro SGML environment for berlin docs ::::


main items of intrest
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

src/		source of documentation (SGML)
html/		output dir for HTML 
print/		output dir for print (PDF)


how it works
~~~~~~~~~~~~

(1) install jade
(2) type "make"
(3) point your browser at html/berlin-man.html


PDF building may or may not work on your machine. I haven't
imported a micro-jadetex distribution in here and I doubt I
will. if you're really anxious for printed docs, mail me and
I'll generate them for you.


customization
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

stylesheets/berlin.dsl	berlin stylesheet customization layer
dtds/berlin.dtd		berlin docbook DTD customization layer



auxilliary stuff
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

stylesheets/		dsssl stylesheets
dtds/			SGML DTDs 
entities/		docbook entities
declarations/		SGML declarations


enjoy
-graydon <graydon@pobox.com>
